HEADWORD: Mockado
<hw>Mock"a*do</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A stuff made in
imitation of velvet; -- probably the same as <altname>mock
velvet</altname>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Our rich <qex>mockado</qex> doublet.</q>
<rj><qau>Ford.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

